				<td colspan="2"><span>I have been looking to upgrade several slots.  My dilema has been determining where my plat would be best spent.
<br />

<br />
I have been toying with upgrading my belt to a soulscream (30k) which is a lot of plat.  Placing stats in that slot is very atractive, but is the haste increase that big a benifit? (vs FBSS)
<br />
Or if I should go for a pair of Valorium rings of galantry.  (20k)
<br />
Or if it is worthwhile to upgrade my wepon to increase dps say wind-worn handblade or copper hammer of striking. (25k &amp; 11k)
<br />

<br />
I have also been looking at my boot, hand, wrist,&amp; neck slots but I dont seem to be able to find anything that will dramaticly increase my stats and or DPS.
<br />

<br />
<a target="_new" href=" http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=974072"> http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=974072</a>
<br />

<br />
Does anyone have suggestions?
<br />

<br />
Thanks in advance.</span></td>
