				<td colspan="2"><span>Your equipment is not much different than mine was at the same level.  If I recall correctly, I was getting pounded on pretty well in LDoN as puller and couldn't really stand up to the mobs to get off my mezz song.
<br />

<br />
Greater AC will be of benefit to you right now.  I'd suggest upgrading where the slots are particularly weak in AC:
<br />

<br />
Wrists x 2: Could be upgraded to cultural for the 25AC and 30HP plus saves.  I wore two rigid steelweaves until I replaced them at lvl 65.
<br />

<br />
Boots:  Steelslave Bladed Boots.  
<br />

<br />
Waist:  I'd really look at a nice belt with AC and stats.
<br />

<br />
